      <title>人民币承压 中国从银行系统撤出现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/china-withdraws-cash-from-banking-system-amid-pressure-on-yuan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着货币贬值压力加大，中国对货币宽松持谨慎态度，已连续第五个月从银行系统提取现金。]]></description>
